Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/gvaughn/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule update --init

To add a new git-based plugin:

    git submodule add https://github.com/tpope/vim-cucumber.git vim/bundle/cucumber

